dc_title_s: Map of Salem and Fenwick Creeks. Salem Co. N.J. showing the Exterior Wharf Line established thereon by the Riparian Commissioners of the State of N.J.
dc_description_s: Sheet 1: Map shows a few roads of Salem City just south of Fenwick Creek and Salem Creek. Map also shows exterior wharf lines established by the Riparian Commissioners of the State of New Jersey.|Sheet 2: Map shows Fenwick Creek and Salem Creek and a few roads of Salem City. Includes wharf lines for the creeks.|Sheet 3: Shows a few roads of Salem City just south of Fenwick Creek and Salem Creek. Includes wharf lines for the creeks.
